            <title>[CASSANDRA-15056] SimpleClient should pass connection properties as options</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15056</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As of today. SimpleClient does not pass CHECKSUM or COMPRESSION as options to the server. In order for these parameters to take effect on the server side, they should be passed as options.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
